# Agents Folder

This folder is reserved for Claude Code agents.

## What are Agents?

Agents are autonomous workflows that can execute multi-step tasks. They go beyond skills by chaining together multiple operations.

## Coming Soon

Agent capabilities include:
- Multi-step content workflows
- Automated content repurposing
- Research and compilation
- Content calendar management
- Batch content generation

## Structure

Each agent will be a folder containing:
- AGENT.md - Agent instructions
- Supporting files as needed

## Note

Agent functionality is an advanced feature. Start with skills first, then add agents as your system matures.
